Description=Select the type of network connection you are on for the best online experience.

[DynamicNetspeed UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Dynamic Netspeed
Description=Toggle whether or not netspeed is dynamic.

[AllowCustomCharacters UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Allow Custom Characters
Description=Toggle whether or not to allow custom characters.

[AlwaysLoadCustomCharacters UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Always Load Custom Characters
Description=Load Custom Characters throughout game (may cause hitching on low-end systems).

;///////////////
; Weapon Options
;///////////////
[CrosshairType UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Crosshair Type
Description=Normal crosshairs are unique to each weapon, Simple crosshairs are the same for all weapons.

[WeaponSwitchOnPickup UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Weapon Switch on Pickup
Description=Toggle whether or not weapons automatically switch upon pickup.

[WeaponHand UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Weapon Hand
Description=Select where the currently equipped weapon is displayed.

[SmallWeapons UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Small Weapons
Description=Toggle whether or not to display a smaller version of your weapon in first person.

[DisplayWeaponBar UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Display Weapon Bar
Description=Toggle whether or not to display your weapon bar.

[ShowOnlyAvailableWeapons UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Only Show Available Weapons
Description=Toggle whether or not to display the empty slots of your weapon bar.

;///////////////
; HUD Options
;///////////////
[RotateMap UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Zoomed Minimap
Description=Toggle whether or not to default to a zoomed-in rotating minimap.

[ShowMap UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Show Map
Description=Toggle whether or not to display the map on the HUD.

[ShowClock UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Show Clock
Description=Toggle whether or not to display the match clock on the HUD.

[ShowDoll UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Show Objective paths
Description=Toggle whether or not to display the paths to objectives (CTF and Warfare).

