[WorldDetail UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
Description=Change the detail of world in-game to presets, or use custom settings below (Static Decals and lower).

[StaticDecals UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Static Decals
Description=Toggles whether or not static decals are shown.

[DynamicDecals UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Dynamic Decals
Description=Toggles whether or not dynamic (weapon fire, blood, etc) decals are shown or not.

[DynamicLights UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Dynamic Lights
Description=Toggles whether or not dynamic lights are used.

[DynamicShadows UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Dynamic Shadows
Description=Toggles whether or not dynamic shadows are shown.

[LightEnvironmentShadows UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Light Environment Shadows
Description=Toggles whether or not certain shadows are shown.

[CompositeDynamicLights UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Disable Composite Dynamic Lights
Description=Toggles whether or not to join multiple dynamic lights together.

[DirectionalLightmaps UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Directional Lightmaps
Description=Toggles whether or not to allow directional based lightmaps (requires restart of the game to take effect).

[Bloom UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Bloom and Depth of Field
Description=Toggles whether or not bloom and depth of field are used.

[QualityBloom UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable High Quality Bloom
Description=Toggles whether or not to use higher quality bloom (if bloom is enabled).

[Distortion UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Distortion
Description=Toggles whether or not distortion effects are used.

[DropParticleDistortion UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Disable Particle Distortion Dropping
Description=Toggles whether or not to allow particles with distortion to be hidden.

[SpeedTreeLeaves UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Speed Tree Leaves
Description=Toggles whether or not to use render the leaves on some trees.

[SpeedTreeFronds UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Speed Tree Fronds
Description=Toggles whether or not to show the branches/fronds on some trees.

[DetailMode UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Detail Mode
Description=Sets the detail level of various aspects throughout the game.

[LensFlares UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Lens Flares
Description=Toggles whether or not lens flares are enabled.

[FogVolumes UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Enable Fog Volumes
Description=Toggles whether or not to enable fog.

[OneFrameThreadLag UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Disable One Frame Thread Lag
Description=Toggles whether the threading timing should be relaxed or strict. Relaxed timing can make the framerate smoother, whereas strict timing can make the game controls more responsive.

[SkeletalMeshLODBias UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Character Model Level of Detail
Description=Sets the character model quality (lower will force lower quality meshes).

[ParticleLODBias UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Effects Level of Detail
Description=Sets the effects quality (lower will force lower quality effects).

[ShadowFilterQualityBias UTUIDataProvider_MenuOption]
FriendlyName=Shadow Quality
Description=Sets the shadow quality (lower will force lower quality shadows).

[SliderValues]
ExtraLow=X-Low
Low=Low
Mid=Mid
High=High

